data.meta_description:
22 likes, 4 comments - amanda_coffee_books on May 29, 2024: "Good Morning  Morning Coffee Friends,
Chocolate Cheesecake hot latte.
I am using Mexican Blend From Sunrise Coffee Collective. I do have some Promo codes in my Linktree. 
I really enjoying my 3 in 1 frappe machine. 
There is so much you can do with this machine. 
Everything I use will always be ⤵️ 
.
.
Ingredients:
4oz Mexican Blend (Sunrise Coffee Collective) 
No bake Cheescake mixed Chocolate sauce sides cup
Chocolate Curls 
1/2 tbsp Chocolate sauce amoretti
1/2 tsp Vanilla mixed with froth amoretti 
1/2 cup Milk froth 
Chocolate Curls on top. 
.
.
Machine Used/tools 
3 in 1 Frappe
